PN,41301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FGlenn Perkins was a firefighter for 22
OL,8,Fyears, used to putting his life on the
OL,9,Fline for others, and a dad to two
OL,10,Fdaughters.
OL,12,FBut he was also a chronic alcoholic
OL,13,Fwho was able to order dozens of
OL,14,Fbottles of alcohol through delivery
OL,15,Fapps.
OL,17,FHe died from alcoholic liver disease
OL,18,Faged 55.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FNow his daughters have released
OL,8,Ffootage of their father in his living
OL,9,Froom, surrounded by carrier bags full
OL,10,Fof beer, spirits and empty bottles, to
OL,11,Fhighlight calls for tighter
OL,12,Frestrictions on food and drink
OL,13,Fdelivery apps.
OL,15,FConnie and Daisy Perkins say Uber Eats
OL,16,Fand other apps gave their dad easy
OL,17,Funlimited access to alcohol delivered
OL,18,Fto his door.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FThey're angry that the deliveries
OL,8,Fcontinued, despite their father's
OL,9,Fobvious drunkenness, and despite them
OL,10,Fbegging Uber Eats to blacklist his
OL,11,Faddress.
OL,13,FUber say they have updated their
OL,14,Fsupport measures but the sisters say
OL,15,Fit needs to go further.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FGlenn said he was suffering from Post-
OL,8,FTraumatic Stress Disorder (PTSD), a
OL,9,Fmental health condition triggered by
OL,10,Fwitnessing a traumatic incident during
OL,11,Fhis time with the fire brigade, which
OL,12,Fled to his alcoholism.
OL,14,FBut his daughters believe their father
OL,15,Fwould have lived far longer had he not
OL,16,Fstarted using fast food apps - giving
OL,17,Fhim effortless round the clock access
OL,18,Fto alcohol deliveries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,F"Originally he was going out and he
OL,8,Fwas having a shower, getting dressed,
OL,9,Fwalking to the shops, getting fresh
OL,10,Fair, but then with these apps he
OL,11,Fdidn't need to do any of that and he
OL,12,Fjust started to decline, he didn't
OL,13,Fneed to leave the house anymore,"
OL,14,FConnie said.
OL,16,F"He was ordering as early as 6am in
OL,17,Fthe morning and then an hour later he
OL,18,Fwas doing another order - continuously
OL,19,Fthroughout the day.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,F"Something needs to stop with the fact
OL,8,Fyou shouldn't be able to keep ordering
OL,9,Falcohol over and over again throughout
OL,10,Fthe day."
OL,12,FConnie and Daisy say they know their
OL,13,Fdad would have been an alcoholic
OL,14,Feither way but believe his condition
OL,15,Fworsened due to the use of the apps.
OL,17,F"These apps made it easier for him to
OL,18,Faccess the alcohol," Connie added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,F"I don't think he would have died as
OL,8,Fsoon as 55 years of age, I think he'd
OL,9,Fstill be here now.
OL,11,F"Yes I do think he would eventually
OL,12,Fdie through alcohol problems, but not
OL,13,Fas early as 55."
OL,15,FThe sisters have revealed their dad
OL,16,Fdidn't leave the house or shower for
OL,17,Fup to four months during the final
OL,18,Fyear of his life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FContinuously in his pyjamas, he spent
OL,8,Fhis days making repeated orders on the
OL,9,Fapps for alcohol.
OL,11,FGlenn even stopped taking the rubbish
OL,12,Fout, resulting in dozens of empty
OL,13,Falcohol bottles left strewn around his
OL,14,Fhome, as well as carrier bags full of
OL,15,Fmore supplies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FDaisy said they repeatedly tried to
OL,8,Fget their dad to stop drinking, by
OL,9,Fremoving his bank cards, and his
OL,10,Fphone, and he even went into rehab,
OL,11,Fbut in the end they were unable to
OL,12,Fstop him.
OL,14,F"My dad couldn't have controlled
OL,15,Fhimself, he was an alcoholic - it's an
OL,16,Fillness, it's not a choice.
OL,18,F"We did check in on him but no matter
OL,19,Fhow many times a day you check in
OL,20,Fthey're always going to pick up the
OL,21,Fdrink.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,F"He didn't want a drink but he had no
OL,8,Fchoice he had to - he physically had
OL,9,Fto drink you know it was a need.
OL,11,F"Towards the end there was no helping
OL,12,Fhim he didn't want the help and you
OL,13,Fcan't help an alcoholic unless they
OL,14,Fwant to."
OL,16,FDaisy and Connie want safer
OL,17,Frestrictions introduced with checks
OL,18,Fcarried out if drivers have concerns
OL,19,Fabout the delivery recipient.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,FThey are taking their campaign to
OL,8,FWestminster next week, and are calling
OL,9,Ffor legal change to protect people
OL,10,Flike their father.
OL,12,FAn Uber Eats spokesperson said: "We
OL,13,Fare very sorry to hear about this
OL,14,Ffamily's loss.
OL,16,F"The safety and well-being of our
OL,17,Fcommunity is our priority and we have
OL,18,Fmade significant updates to our
OL,19,Fsupport measures on this issue in
OL,20,Frecent years.
OL,26,@tD@aOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775153467
OL,3,CDelivery apps let dad buy alcohol
OL,4,C'continuously' until his death, say
OL,5,Cdaughters
OL,7,F"This includes placing restrictions on
OL,8,Fplatform access for customers where
OL,9,Fnecessary and an ongoing partnership
OL,10,Fwith Drinkaware to implement further
OL,11,Falcohol safety measures, including
OL,12,Fclear signposting to support resources.
OL,14,F"To help ensure responsible
OL,15,Fconsumption, every alcohol delivery
OL,16,Frequires the courier to confirm the
OL,17,Frecipient's date of birth as per their
OL,18,Fphysical ID and conduct a sobriety
OL,19,Fcheck before an order can be
OL,20,Fcompleted."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/13
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
